<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Khumalo Craft Emporium</title>
    <style>

        section {
            background-color: black; /* Set white background for sections */
            color: white; /* Set text color to black within sections */
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px auto; /* Add more space between sections and center them */
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 50%; /* Set width to 50% */
        }

            section p {
                font-size: 1.1em; /* Increase font size of paragraph text */
            }

        header h1 {
            background-color: #FF6600;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5px;
            margin: 10px auto; /* Center align the h1 */
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: fit-content; /* Adjust width to fit content */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Khumalo Craft Emporium</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>
                Founded by visionary entrepreneur James Khumalo, our vision is to establish Khumalo Craft Emporium as a premier global e-commerce platform for handcrafted products. We strive to create a scalable, accessible, and user-friendly platform that empowers artisans and delights customers.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Explore Our Collection</h2>
            <p>
                Browse through our curated collection of handcrafted products, ranging from exquisite textiles to intricately carved woodwork. Each piece is a testament to the skill and creativity of artisans from diverse cultures and backgrounds.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Support Artisans Worldwide</h2>
            <p>
                By shopping at Khumalo Craft Emporium, you're not just purchasing a product - you're supporting artisans and their communities worldwide. We prioritize fair trade practices and ethical sourcing, ensuring that artisans receive fair compensation for their work.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
            <p>
                Become part of our global community of artisans, customers, and supporters. Sign up for our newsletter to stay updated on the latest additions to our collection, exclusive offers, and artisan spotlights.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Start Exploring</h2>
            <p>
                Begin your journey into the world of artisanal craftsmanship with Khumalo Craft Emporium. Discover unique treasures, support talented artisans, and celebrate the beauty of handmade creations.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
